Center: US National Nuclear Data Center, Brookhaven, USA
title: Interaction of neutrons with matter.

x4codes.hlp: Columbia University, New York, NY, United States of America

x4freetext: Measurements were made for slow and fast neutrons,
the exact neutron energies were not determined.
0.025 eV for slow neutrons and 5 MeV for fast
neutrons are entered by the compiler.
Natural samples or compounds were used.
Errors are of the order of 10 percent for lower
cross sections and about 25 percent for the larger
Data taken from Table IV of the journal article.
Data at 5 MeV deleted. Not this experiment.
DR Format updated and reference corrected
